Description:
SAPSPACES is a platform that provides a range of services to SAP customers, including **freelance hiring**, **online courses**, and **consulting services**. The platform has more than **10,000 SAP freelancers** in **22 different countries**¬π. SAP consultants provide many services to companies in various units, where you can search for the services your company needs and purchase them immediately. You can also communicate directly with SAP consultants¬π.

SAPSPACES was originally known for leadership in enterprise resource planning (ERP) software. The platform has since expanded to offer a range of services, including **SAP S/4HANA**, **SAP Business ByDesign**, and **SAP SuccessFactors**¬π. SAP S/4HANA is SAP's ERP for large enterprises. It is the successor of SAP R/3 and SAP ERP and is optimized for SAP's in-memory database SAP HANA¬π. SAP Business ByDesign is a cloud enterprise resource planning software that is sold and operated as software as a service by SAP SE. It is designed for small and medium-sized enterprises¬π. SAP SuccessFactors is a cloud-based software for human capital management using the Software as a service model¬π.

SAPSPACES also provides a community platform where SAP customers can obtain support from each other. Users can add topics or questions that need solutions or suggestions, or follow up on the new technical features of SAP via the SAP community¬π. The platform also offers technical articles on various topics related to SAP, such as payroll schemas, personnel calculation rules, and leading ledger selection for parallel accounting in S/4HANA Cloud, Public Edition¬π.

If you are interested in SAPSPACES, you can register as a freelancer or identify your company profile and get a free package with your own control panel to run your business. The platform also offers a range of services, including **SAP Mobile APPS**, **SAP Digital Marketing**, and **SAP BUSINESS ONE**¬π. You can also email the platform at Info@sapspaces.com for more information¬π.
